title: RocketTheme RT Osmosis Joomla 2.5-3.x Template
description:
Osmosis follows a vibrant, but elegant design direction, allowing for full width beautiful backgrounds in the header, fixing them as the site's focal point. An excellent method of making the template unique with a few simple steps.

The sidepanel is a configurable feature of the template, which dynamically unveils content within automatically during scroll. Prebuilt logo and vertically opening dropdown menu features are available, as well as normal modules types.

Osmosis debuts a new responsive layout type: Fluid; in addition to the normal responsive layout type. This layout adapts to the full width of the browser window, whilst still supporting normal responsive modes such as mobile and tablet.

The template has an array of subtle, non-intrusive but visually engaging content animations to provide a layer of additional interaction to your page. These do not detract from the content, allowing its importance to not be diluted by visual effects.
